      <h1>Collaborating with Swiss Filmmakers: What to Know</h1>
      <p class="lead">Learn how collaborating with Swiss filmmakers gives you access to top talent, film funding schemes, and tax incentives for your next project.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>January 8, 2025</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 24, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
